#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.appearance.gschema.xml.in.h:1
msgid "File to use for the desktop background image."
msgstr "桌面背景图片的文件路径。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.appearance.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid "File to use for the lock screen background image."
msgstr "锁屏背景图片的文件路径。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.appearance.gschema.xml.in.h:3
msgid "Whether turn on automatic window theme switching according to time."
msgstr "是否根据时间开启自动窗口主题切换。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.appearance.gschema.xml.in.h:4
msgid "Whether show desktop background."
msgstr "是否显示桌面背景。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.display.gschema.xml.in.h:1
msgid "Layout of connected monitors in the screen."
msgstr "已连接的显示器在屏幕中的位置布局。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.display.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid ""
"It takes effect immediately when the scaling factor of window is changed."
msgstr "当窗口缩放率发生变化时立即生效。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.display.gschema.xml.in.h:3
msgid "Set whether to adapt to screen changes"
msgstr "设置是否适应屏幕变化"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.display.gschema.xml.in.h:4
msgid "Set max screen record number while save config."
msgstr "保存配置时设置最大屏幕记录数量。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keyboard.gschema.xml.in.h:1
msgid "Whether enable capslock and numlock windows tips."
msgstr "是否启用大写锁定和数字锁定窗口提示。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keyboard.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid "Whether enable capslock tips."
msgstr "是否启用大写锁定提示。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keyboard.gschema.xml.in.h:3
msgid "Whether enable numlock tips."
msgstr "是否启用数字锁定提示。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keyboard.gschema.xml.in.h:4
msgid ""
"Whether repeat to trigger KeyPress and KeyRelease event when key is pressed."
msgstr "当键被长按后是否重复触发按下和弹起事件。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keyboard.gschema.xml.in.h:5
msgid ""
"The delay time in ms after the initial press of an auto-repeating key and "
"the first generated repeat event."
msgstr "当键被按下时第一次触发按下事件的延时(毫秒)。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keyboard.gschema.xml.in.h:6
msgid "The delay time in ms between all subsequent generated repeat events."
msgstr "当键被按下后每个按键(按下或者弹起)事件之间的间隔时间。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keyboard.gschema.xml.in.h:7
msgid "Keyboard layouts."
msgstr "键盘布局。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keyboard.gschema.xml.in.h:8
msgid "Keyboard options."
msgstr "键盘选项。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:1
msgid "Volume step"
msgstr "音量步进"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid "Volume step as percentage of volume."
msgstr "以音量百分比步进音量。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:3
msgid "Toggle touchpad"
msgstr "触摸板开关"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:4
msgid "Binding to enable or disable the touchpad."
msgstr "启用或禁用触摸板的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:5
msgid "Enable touchpad"
msgstr "启用触摸板"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:6
msgid "Binding to enable the touchpad."
msgstr "启用触摸板的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:7
msgid "Disable touchpad"
msgstr "关闭触摸板"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:8
msgid "Binding to disable the touchpad."
msgstr "禁用触摸板的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:9
msgid "Shut down"
msgstr "关机"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:10
msgid "Binding to shut down."
msgstr "关机的键绑定"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:11
msgid "Log out"
msgstr "注销"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:12
msgid "Binding to log out."
msgstr "注销的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:13
msgid "Home folder"
msgstr "主文件夹"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:14
msgid "Binding to open the Home folder."
msgstr "打开主文件夹的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:15
msgid "Launch email client"
msgstr "启动电子邮件客户端"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:16
msgid "Binding to launch the email client."
msgstr "调用电子邮件客户端的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:17
msgid "Lock screen"
msgstr "锁住屏幕"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:18
msgid "Binding to lock the screen."
msgstr "锁住屏幕的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:19
msgid "Show desktop"
msgstr "显示桌面"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:20
msgid "Binding to show the desktop."
msgstr "显示桌面的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:21
msgid "Launch help browser"
msgstr "启动帮助浏览器"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.keys.gschema.xml.in.h:22
msgid "Binding to launch the help browser."
msgstr "调用帮助浏览器的键绑定。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.mouse.gschema.xml.in.h:1
#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.touchpad.gschema.xml.in.h:1
msgid "Swap left and right buttons for left-handed."
msgstr "启动左手模式后，左右键功能进行切换。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.mouse.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid "Acceleration multiplier for mouse motion."
msgstr "鼠标移动加速。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.mouse.gschema.xml.in.h:3
msgid ""
"Enables middle mouse button emulation through simultaneous left and right "
"button click."
msgstr "通过同时左键和右键启用鼠标中键模拟按钮点击。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.mouse.gschema.xml.in.h:4
#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.touchpad.gschema.xml.in.h:6
msgid ""
"Enables or disables natural scroll. Natural scrolling is the terminology for "
"moving the content in the direction of scrolling, i.e. moving the wheel or "
"fingers down moves the page down."
msgstr ""
"启用或禁用自然滚动。自然滚动是沿滚动方向移动内容，即移动滚轮或手指向下时页面"
"向下移动。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:1
msgid "The idle timeout when uses battery to supply for computer."
msgstr "使用电池供电时计算机的空闲超时时间。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid "The triggered action when uses battery to supply for computer."
msgstr "使用电池供电时计算机触发的动作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:3
msgid "The idle timeout when uses ac to supply for computer."
msgstr "使用交流电源供电时计算机的空闲超时时间。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:4
msgid "The triggered action when uses ac to supply for computer.."
msgstr "使用交流电源供电时计算机触发的动作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:5
msgid "The idle timeout when uses battery to supply for backlight device."
msgstr "使用电池供电时背光设备的空闲超时时间。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:6
msgid "The triggered action when uses battery to supply for backlight device."
msgstr "使用电池供电时背光设备触发的动作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:7
msgid "The idle timeout when uses ac to supply for backlight device."
msgstr "使用交流电源供电时背光设备的空闲超时时间。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:8
msgid "The triggered action when uses ac to supply for backlight device."
msgstr "使用交流电源供电时背光设备触发的动作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:9
msgid ""
"The percentage of brightness displayed when the battery is low or the "
"computer is idle."
msgstr "当电池电量低或计算机空闲时显示的亮度百分比。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:10
msgid "Whether does the display darken when the computer is idle."
msgstr "计算机空闲时显示器是否变暗。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:11
msgid "Whether does the display darken when the ups or battery power is low."
msgstr "当UPS或电池电量低时显示器是否变暗。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:12
msgid "Whether does the cpu save energy when the ups or battery power is low."
msgstr "当UPS或电池电量低时CPU是否节能。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:13
msgid "The action to take when the system suspend button is pressed."
msgstr "按下系统挂起按钮时要执行的操作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:14
msgid "The action to take when the system hibernate button is pressed."
msgstr "按下系统休眠按钮时要执行的操作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:15
msgid "The action to take when the system power button is pressed."
msgstr "按下系统电源按钮时要执行的操作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:16
msgid "The action to take when the laptop lid is closed."
msgstr "笔记本电脑盖子关闭时要执行的操作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:17
msgid "The action to take when the UPS power is critical."
msgstr "UPS电源电量严重不足时要执行的操作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:18
msgid "The action to take when the battery power is critical."
msgstr "电池电量严重不足时要执行的操作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:19
msgid "Set the policy for obtaining brightness values."
msgstr "设置获取亮度值的策略。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.power.gschema.xml.in.h:20
msgid "The profiles daemon used by current power plugin."
msgstr "当前电源插件使用的配置守护进程。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.session-daemon.gschema.xml.in.h:1
msgid "Enabled plugins list."
msgstr "已启用的插件列表。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.session-daemon.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid "Disabled plugins list which prior to enabled plugins list."
msgstr "在启用插件列表之前的已禁用插件列表。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:1
msgid ""
"Maximum time allowed between two clicks for them to be considered a double "
"click (in milliseconds)."
msgstr "触发双击事件时两次单击之间允许的最大时间 (毫秒)。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid ""
"Maximum distance allowed between two clicks for them to be considered a "
"double click (in pixels)."
msgstr "触发双击事件时两次单击之间允许的最大距离 (像素)。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:3
msgid "Number of pixels the cursor can move before dragging."
msgstr "拖动前光标可以移动的像素数。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:4
msgid "Whether the cursor should blink."
msgstr "光标是否应该闪烁。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:5
msgid "Length of the cursor blink cycle, in milleseconds."
msgstr "光标闪烁周期的长度 (毫秒)。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:6
msgid "Name of gtk theme to use."
msgstr "系统使用的主题。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:7
msgid "Name of icon theme to use for icons."
msgstr "系统使用的图标主题。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:8
msgid "Whether to play sounds on user events."
msgstr "是否在用户事件中播放声音。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:9
msgid "The XDG sound theme to use for event sounds."
msgstr "用于事件声音的XDG声音主题。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:10
msgid "Whether to play sounds on input events."
msgstr "是否在输入事件上播放声音。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:11
msgid "Whether to antialias Xft fonts; 0=no, 1=yes, -1=default."
msgstr "是否开启Xft字体抗锯齿；-1表示默认值。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:12
msgid "Whether to hint Xft fonts; 0=no, 1=yes, -1=default."
msgstr "是否开启Xft字体微调；-1表示默认值。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:13
msgid ""
"What degree of hinting to use; \"hintnone\", \"hintslight\", \"hintmedium\", "
"or \"hintfull\"."
msgstr "使用什么程度的微调。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:14
msgid ""
"Type of subpixel antialiasing; \"rgba\", \"rgb\", \"bgr\", \"vrgb\", "
"\"vbgr\"."
msgstr "子像素抗锯齿类型；\"rgba\"、\"rgb\"、\"bgr\"、\"vrgb\"、\"vbgr\"。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:15
msgid ""
"Resolution for Xft, in 1024 * dots/inch. -1 to use default value. Do not "
"modify it manually."
msgstr "字体分辨率，请不要手动修改。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:16
msgid ""
"The resolution used for converting font sizes to pixel sizes, in dots per "
"inch."
msgstr "用于将字体大小转换为像素大小的分辨率，单位为每英寸点数。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:17
msgid "Name of the cursor theme."
msgstr "光标主题。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:18
msgid "Size of the cursor referenced by cursor_theme."
msgstr "光标大小。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:19
msgid ""
"Time in seconds after which the cursor is hidden when blinking is enabled."
msgstr "启用光标闪烁时，光标隐藏前的秒数。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:20
msgid "Name of default font to use."
msgstr "GTK默认字体。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:21
msgid "Name of key theme RC file to load."
msgstr "GTK要加载的关键主题的名称。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:22
msgid ""
"Whether default toolbars have text only, text and icons, icons only, etc."
msgstr "默认工具栏是否只有文本、文本和图标、图标。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:23
msgid "Size of icons in default toolbars."
msgstr "默认工具栏中图标的大小。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:24
msgid "How to draw the input method preedit string."
msgstr "如何绘制输入法预编辑字符串。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:25
msgid "How to draw the input method statusbar."
msgstr "如何绘制输入法状态栏。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:26
msgid "Name of the input method module used by GTK+."
msgstr "GTK使用的输入法模块的名称。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:27
msgid "Whether images should be shown in menus."
msgstr "是否应在菜单中显示图像。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:28
msgid "Whether stock icons should be shown in buttons."
msgstr "图像是否显示在按钮中。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:29
msgid "The accelerator for moving the focus to the menubar."
msgstr "将焦点移动到菜单栏的加速器"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:30
msgid ""
"A '\\n' separated list of \"name:color\" as defined by the 'gtk-color-"
"scheme' setting"
msgstr "颜色主题"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:31
msgid ""
"Module to use as the filesystem model for the GtkFileChooser widget. "
"Possible values are \"gio\" and \"gtk+\"."
msgstr "用作GtkFileChooser小部件的文件系统模型的模块"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:32
msgid ""
"This setting determines which buttons should be put in the titlebar of "
"client-side decorated windows, and whether they should be placed at the left "
"of right."
msgstr ""
"此设置确定哪些按钮应放在客户端装饰窗口的标题栏中，以及是否应放在右侧的左侧。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:33
msgid ""
"This setting determines where application menu will be displayed - in a "
"window or on a panel with MenuModel protocol."
msgstr ""
"此设置确定应用程序菜单的显示位置，在窗口中或使用MenuModel协议的面板上。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:34
msgid ""
"This setting determines where window menubars will be displayed - in a "
"window or on a panel with MenuModel protocol."
msgstr "此设置确定窗口菜单栏的显示位置，在窗口中或使用MenuModel协议的面板上"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:35
msgid ""
"Whether the context menus of entries and text views should offer to change "
"the input method."
msgstr "条目和文本视图的上下文菜单是否应提供更改输入法的功能。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:36
msgid ""
"Whether the context menus of entries and text views should offer to insert "
"control characters."
msgstr "条目和文本视图的上下文菜单是否应提供更改输入法的功能。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:37
msgid ""
"Whether mnemonics should be automatically shown and hidden when the user "
"presses the Alt key."
msgstr "当用户按Alt键时，助记符是否应自动显示和隐藏。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:38
msgid ""
"If true, gtk+ uses the primary paste selection, usually triggered by a "
"middle mouse button click."
msgstr "如果为true，gtk+将使用主粘贴选择，通常由鼠标中键单击触发。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:39
msgid "Whether to enable toolkit-wide animations."
msgstr "是否启用工具箱范围的动画。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:40
msgid ""
"Whether builtin GTK+ dialogs such as the file chooser, the color chooser or "
"the font chooser will use a header bar at the top to show action widgets, or "
"an action area at the bottom."
msgstr ""
"无论是内置的GTK+对话框、文件选择器、颜色选择器或字体选择器，都将使用顶部的标"
"题栏或者底部的操作区域来显示操作小部件。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:41
msgid ""
"This controls the GTK scale factor that maps from window coordinates to the "
"actual device pixels."
msgstr "控制从窗口坐标映射到实际设备像素的GTK比例因子。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:42
msgid ""
"This setting determines whether MATE controls the scale factor for QT "
"applications."
msgstr "此设置确定MATE是否控制QT应用程序的比例因子。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.settings.gschema.xml.in.h:43
msgid "Reload marco, caja and panel when window scaling factor is changed."
msgstr "窗口缩放因子改变时重新加载marco、caja和panel。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.touchpad.gschema.xml.in.h:2
msgid "Indicates if diable while typing is enabled or disabled."
msgstr "打字时禁用触摸板功能。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.touchpad.gschema.xml.in.h:3
msgid ""
"Set this to TRUE to be able to send mouse clicks by tapping on the touchpad."
msgstr "设置为真则表示轻击触摸板触发对应的鼠标事件，例如双击等同于鼠标右键。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.touchpad.gschema.xml.in.h:4
msgid ""
"Enables a click method. Permitted methods are buttonareas and clickfinger, "
"respectively conreesponding to 0 and 1."
msgstr "设置单击方法。可通过按下和轻触的方式触发点击事件。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.touchpad.gschema.xml.in.h:5
msgid ""
"Enables a scroll method. Permitted methods are twofinger, edge and button, "
"respectively conrresponding to 0, 1 and 2."
msgstr ""
"设置滚动方法。可通过双指滑动、边缘滑动和按键(键盘中间的红色按钮)的方式触发滚"
"动操作。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.touchpad.gschema.xml.in.h:7
msgid "Set this to TRUE to enable all touchpads."
msgstr "开启或关闭触摸板。"

#: ../data/schemas/com.kylinsec.kiran.touchpad.gschema.xml.in.h:8
msgid "Acceleration multiplier for touchpad motion."
msgstr "触摸板移动加速。"

